{"tid":1966150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台調查局：中國網軍假冒台灣網友攻擊譚德塞","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T04:04:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"468ecbf5633c2c644bb5170f444cdb2467f97940","tid":1966150,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"在台北，法務部調查局表示，查獲大陸網軍假冒台灣網民攻擊世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞，將於今日稍後召開記者會說明。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞早前在世衛日內瓦總部的例行記者會上，指責台灣過去3個月對他人身攻擊。台灣的外交部門提出嚴正抗議，要求譚德塞立即更正毫無依據的指控並道歉。蔡英文總統亦對於台灣被指控發動種族歧視攻擊的言論，表達強烈抗議。她說，計劃邀請譚德塞訪問台灣，感受台灣人民如何努力在遭受歧視和孤立之中，堅持走向世界、貢獻國際社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519978-20200410.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519978-20200410.htm&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi64Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=0a9d6c43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519978-20200410.htm&h=bc46a4c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519978-20200410.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c7482e3ae7ffda7ed1e4e775dab380bfcf364e11","tid":1966150,"uid":165750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"識玩"}]}